# Advanced Finance Analytics using MySQL

This project focuses on building an enterprise-style finance and sales analytics system using advanced SQL concepts.

## Features
- Gross & Net Sales Reporting
- Pre/Post Invoice Discount Calculations
- Top Customers & Market Analysis
- Stored Procedures & SQL Views
- Window Functions
- Query Performance Optimization

## SQL Concepts Used
- JOINs
- CTEs
- Window Functions
- Stored Procedures
- User Defined Functions
- Views
- Query Optimization

## Business Insights
- Top Markets by Revenue
- Customer Sales Contribution
- Product Performance Rankings
- Regional Sales Distribution
